<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Macmed details capitalisation award.</title>
<headline>Macmed details capitalisation award.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Macmed Health Care Ltd said on Friday it had resolved to award a capitalisation share award of new fully paid shares of five cents each.</p>
<p>The ratio would be 0.588 new shares for every 100 Macmed shares held by shareholders registered on June 6.</p>
<p>Shareholders would be entitled to elect to receive instead a final cash dividend of two cents per Macmed share, the group said.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
